---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Video Analysis">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Video Upload Date Analysis</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-dim)] mb-12">
      Did winners start working on their projects before the challenge began?
      We checked every winner's video upload dates against edition start dates.
    </p>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-accent)]/20 bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2">Verdict</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">No evidence</strong> any winner had videos uploaded before their challenge start date.
        All timestamped evidence points to work happening <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">during the challenge window</strong>.
        The "early posting advantage" refers to submitting early within the window, not to pre-existing work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-accent)]">Methodology</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-dim)] leading-relaxed mb-8">
      We used five search strategies to find videos for every known winner:
      Playwright page scraping of project pages, YouTube JSON-LD metadata extraction,
      X/Twitter search, direct YouTube search, and Figma blog quote analysis.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-accent)]">Findings</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] mb-12">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Project</th>
            <th>Creator</th>
            <th>Edition</th>
            <th>Video Found</th>
            <th>Upload Date</th>
            <th>Days from Start</th>
            <th>Evidence</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-medium">Common Thread</td>
            <td>Charlota Blunarova</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Mar 2026</td>
            <td>No</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">Interactive figma.site prototype only</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-medium">TOKYO</td>
            <td>Kiel Cole</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Mar 2026</td>
            <td>No</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">Interactive figma.site prototype only</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-medium">Pucker</td>
            <td>Aleyna Catak</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Mar 2026</td>
            <td>No</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">Creator stated she built it in a single day during the makeathon</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-medium">Airwwave</td>
            <td>Lee Black</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Mar 2026</td>
            <td>No</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">Interactive figma.site prototype only</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-medium">Duet Booth</td>
            <td>Paige Latimer</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Mar 2026</td>
            <td>No</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">Interactive figma.site prototype only</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-[var(--color-bg)]">
            <td class="font-medium">Reframe It</td>
            <td>Dann Petty</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Mar 2026</td>
            <td class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">Yes</td>
            <td>Mar 4, 2026</td>
            <td>+31 days</td>
            <td class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">Tutorial/demo posted mid-challenge. Challenge ran Feb 1 - Mar 16.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-medium">Web Poetry</td>
            <td>Cara Ellis</td>
            <td class="text-xs">Sep 2025</td>
            <td>No</td>
