    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6">
      <h3 class="font-medium mb-3">On-the-Record Quotes</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-dim)]">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pl-4">
          <p class="italic mb-1">"Figma Make really accelerated the execution of her idea, allowing her to build Pucker in a single day."</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-subtle)]">Figma Blog, about Aleyna Catak (Pucker)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pl-4">
          <p class="italic mb-1">"Starting with pen and paper, Cara sketched out her vision several times before turning to Figma."</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-subtle)]">Figma Blog, about Cara Ellis (Web Poetry)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
